Agency Ad Accounts come straight from Meta Business Partners, which puts them among the strongest, most reliable accounts you can run. When standard accounts buckle under pressure, these keep going, with an **Unlimited Daily Spending Limit** to match.

### At a glance

| Spec | Detail |
| --- | --- |
| **Source** | Meta Business Partner |
| **Daily spending limit** | Unlimited (DSL) |
| **Shared to** | Your own Business Manager |
| **From** | $250 |

### Why advertisers choose them

1. **Exceptional trust and stability** for demanding campaigns.
2. **Unlimited spending limit**, scale without hitting a cap.
3. **Better ad approval rates** and faster review.
4. **More resistant to restrictions** than standard accounts.
5. **Flexible**, suitable for both Greyhat and Blackhat campaigns.

The setup is simple: after payment you share your BM ID, we grant the Agency Ad Account directly to your BM, and you manage everything yourself.

{% callout variant="tip" title="When to choose an Agency Ad Account" %}
Pick this when you need maximum reliability, room to scale spend with no daily cap, and resilience against the restrictions that regularly take down standard accounts. Check current pricing on our [pricing page](https://goadsagency.com/pricing).
{% /callout %}
